Women want power!  They have it!<br><br>
There is no greater power or responsibility on earth than the influence that a Mom has over little boys... the same little boys who become good men and bad men.<br><br>
The infinite patience, firm resolve, tenacity of spirit and gentle love so amply demonstrated by my mother was fundamental in conveying a sense of right and wrong to me.  Her strength and courage as a &quot;Mom&quot; and housewife mocks the antics of those women today who choose to demonstrate strength by being combat soldiers..corporate executives or anything other than taking on the toughest job on earth..being a good mother.<br><br>
You are honored here as a leader, female, woman, Lady, Pack Mom, mentor, executive, manager, authority, friend, confidant, and person by some of the toughest men on earth.<br><br>
It is strange how real men love real women... it is the counterfeits of both sexes who seem to have the problems.<br><br>
Welcome aboard.  Thanks for the finesse and prudence that good moms generally dispense with such great fecundity.<br><br>
